text: "La La Land" is a song by American singer and rapper Bryce Vine featuring American rapper YG, released through Sire Records on February 28, 2019, as the second single from Vine's debut album Carnival. It debuted at number 92 on the US Billboard Hot 100 in June 2019. ==Charts== {| class="wikitable sortable plainrowheaders" style="text-align:center" |- ! scope="col"| Chart (2019) ! scope="col"| Peak position |- |- |- |- ! scope="row"| US Rolling Stone Top 100 | 59 |} ==Certifications== ==References== Category:2019 singles Category:2019 songs Category:Bryce Vine songs Category:YG (rapper) songs Category:Songs written by Sir Nolan Category:Songs written by YG (rapper)
